textContent:
Feeling inadequate because the answers are taking longer to fill in and I am not staying up late to get them done 

Feeling ashamed that I have chosen to prioritize working with Arielle in person instead of advocating for my need to work individually 

Feeling ashamed about feeling ashamed 

Feeling sad that I don't feel a powerful calming or wholeness with Gil yet 

Feeling anxious that I haven't sent out the agenda for the task force meeting. Feeling anxious I haven't prepped for the conversation with Cyndy.
